{"id":724699,"date":[{"year":1986,"month":5,"day":27}],"page":"2","source":"《文汇月刊》","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"117","ytitle":"","mtitle":"遐想录","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1986\\05\\865R021701.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>不要老是责备这里脏那里也脏，先得看看自己的眼镜干净否?</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1986\\05\\865R021702.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>烧香的概念已与开后门联系在一起了。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1986\\05\\865R021703.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>河豚与烟斗说:“你我本质一样，只是效率快慢而已。”</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1986\\05\\865R021704.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>周松生</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>公家碗拿来别作他用，这也是一种专业不对口吧!(原载《文汇月刊》第五期)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周松生作</FONT>"}]}